embeds.title: **Offical Free Games Codes Bot**
embeds.description:
:white_check_mark: [Click Here](https://freegames.codes/discord/) for a list of commands 

:round_pushpin: **!test** Send a test message to your current game-deals text channel `!help test` 

:round_pushpin:**!change**  You can set which text channel you want to receive free game deals.  `!help change`

:round_pushpin:**!cat**  You can set from which categories you want to receive messages. `!help cat`

 :round_pushpin: **!prefix** You can set bot prefix.  `!help prefix`

 :round_pushpin: **!notify** You can set which roles will be notified when there is a new deal. `!help notify`

:gift: **!lastgames** Display latest 10 free games  

:lock: **!admin**  Admin lock is a RECOMMENDED feature. You can set which user roles can change the bot settings. `!help admin`

 :map: **!lang** You can change language of the bot. `!help lang`

:information_source: **!info** Display your default settings `!help info`

:cinema: **!video** Tutorial video about how to use the bot. `!help video`
